---
layout: base.njk
title: Conditions
description: Cat health conditions covered on Paws Beyond Odds — from CKD to diabetes, cancer, hyperthyroidism, FIV, and mystery illness.
pageClass: conditions-index
---

<div class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-inner">
    <div class="eyebrow">By condition</div>
    <h1>Find your cat's situation</h1>
    <p>Every condition here has been lived with by one of our cats. This isn't textbook information — it's hard-won knowledge from the exam table, the 2am panic, and the trial and error.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="conditions-section">
  <div class="conditions-inner">

    {% for condition in conditions %}
      {% if condition.featured %}
      <a href="{{ ('/conditions/' + condition.slug + '/') | url }}" class="condition-card condition-featured">
        <span class="cond-icon">{{ condition.icon }}</span>
        <div class="cond-body">
          <div class="cond-kicker">Most comprehensive section</div>
          <h2 class="cond-name">{{ condition.name }}</h2>
          <p class="cond-tagline">{{ condition.tagline }}</p>
          <p class="cond-desc">{{ condition.description }}</p>
          {% if condition.relatedCats %}
          <div class="cond-cats">
            {% for catName in condition.relatedCats %}
            <span class="cond-cat-chip">{{ catName }}</span>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
          {% endif %}
          <span class="cond-link">Explore {{ condition.shortName }} →</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}

    <div class="conditions-grid">
      {% for condition in conditions %}
        {% if not condition.featured %}
        <a href="{{ ('/conditions/' + condition.slug + '/') | url }}" class="condition-card">
          <span class="cond-icon">{{ condition.icon }}</span>
          <h3 class="cond-name">{{ condition.name }}</h3>
          <p class="cond-tagline">{{ condition.tagline }}</p>
          {% if condition.relatedCats %}
          <div class="cond-cats">
            {% for catName in condition.relatedCats %}
            <span class="cond-cat-chip">{{ catName }}</span>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
          {% endif %}
          <span class="cond-link">Explore →</span>
        </a>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<section class="conditions-advocate-cta">
  <div class="cta-inner">
    <div class="cta-icon">💬</div>
    <div>
      <h2>Don't know what's wrong yet?</h2>
      <p>If your cat is declining and you don't have a clear diagnosis, start with the vet advocacy toolkit — it's built for exactly that situation.</p>
      <a href="{{ '/advocate/' | url }}" class="btn btn-outline">Go to the Vet Toolkit →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
